located at the western foothills of the Mount Hermon now under
Israeli occupation, is Lebanon's.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the Qatari cabinet called for a resumption of
negotiations on all tracks in order to achieve a full and
comprehensive peace in the Middle East region, Kuwait News Agency
reported.
</P>
<P>
