<HEADLINE> Pakistan believes There Is Only One China: Spokesman </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, May 31 (Xinhua) -- Pakistan Wednesday said Taiwan is
an integral part of China and the recent statements of Chen
Shuibian of Taiwan are evasive and betray his lack of sincerity
about "One China" policy.
</P>
<P>
"Pakistan believes that there is only one China," Foreign
Office spokesman Iftikhar Murshid said in a statement.
</P>
<P>
He said, "Taiwan is an integral and inalienable part of the
People's Republic of China, which is the sole legal government
representing the whole of China including Taiwan."
</P>
<P>
He said the Taiwan issue is an internal affair of the People's
Republic of China. "Outside powers should not meddle in China's
internal affairs."
</P>
<P>
"The government of Pakistan is confident that like Hong Kong
and Macao, Taiwan would soon return to the motherland," he added.
</P>
</TEXT>
