<HEADLINE> Jiang's Thinking New Development of Marxist Party Building Theory: Commentary (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 31 (Xinhua) -- The recent important thinking of
Jiang Zemin, general secretary of the Communist Party of China (
CPC) Central Committee, represents a new development of Marxist
Party-building theory, a Xinhua commentary says today.
</P>
<P>
During a recent inspection tour of south China's Guangdong
Province, Jiang said the key to running China lies in the CPC, in
its ideology, style of work, organization, discipline, and
capabilities and leadership.
</P>
<P>
The CPC will remain successful and enjoy the heartfelt support
of the people of China so long as the Party always earnestly
represents the requirements of developing China's advanced social
productive forces, the progressive course of China's advanced
culture, and the fundamental interests of the Chinese people,
Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
Jiang's important thinking summed up the historic experience of
the CPC over the past 80 years, analyzed the lessons of the world'
s socialist movement, and answered questions the CPC has
encountered in the country's reform and opening up and
modernization drive.
</P>
<P>
The thinking also displays the spirit of emancipating the mind
and seeking truth from facts, and will serve as the guiding
principle for Party-building in the new situation, the commentary
stresses.
</P>
<P>
The commentary notes that Jiang's thinking is, first of all, a
high and thorough condensation of the CPC's advanced features. (
more)
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE20000531.0188 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-31 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang's Thinking New Development of Marxist Party Building Theory: Commentary (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The CPC is the political leader and advanced representative of
the working class, and its advanced features can vary from time to
time.
</P>
<P>
Summing up the experience of the world's socialist movement,
Jiang's thinking has brought to light the essence and implications
of the Party's advanced features, and deepened the Party's
understanding of itself.
</P>
<P>
That is, the Party must always earnestly represent the
requirements of developing China's advanced social productive
forces, the progressive course of China's advanced culture, and
the fundamental interests of the Chinese people.
</P>
<P>
Jiang's thinking has also enriched and deepened the contents of
the Party building, the commentary says.
</P>
<P>
During the revolutionary period and in times of war, the goal
of Party building was to build up a political force that could
lead the people forward and overthrow the reactionary rule. After
taking power, the Party had shifted the goal to building itself
into a strong leader of socialist construction.
</P>
<P>
Jiang's thinking has charted the orientation for Party building
in the new century and for the advancement of China's reform and
opening to the outside world as well as its ongoing modernization
drive led by the Party, the commentary states.
</P>
<P>
While emphasizing Jiang's thinking as a new development of
Marxist Party-building theory, the commentary calls on the whole
Party to conscientiously study the "three representatives"
thinking and take concrete measures to push forward the great
cause of building socialism with Chinese characteristics. 
</P>
</TEXT>
