defeat the
financial dictatorship," and announced a general strike on June 9.
</P>
<P>
An IMF mission arrived Tuesday night in the country to monitor
the compliance with the budget targets agreed on by the Argentine
government with the international entity.
</P>
<P>
The Argentine government announced Monday a package of
adjustment measures, with a reduction of public servants' salaries
and retirement funds as the nucleus, to reduce the budget deficit.
